categories: Category:Victory-class Star Destroyers of the Galactic Empire

nodes.text: The Subjugator was a Victory-class Star Destroyer under the command of Captain Kolaff. Juren was the ship's Chief Engineer.

Subjugator was deployed in the Relgim sector. It was later sent to Kwenn Space Station by Lira and Denn Wessex to capture Walex Blissex. Blissex and a group of Alliance agents were captured, but managed to escape.
It was engaged by a Rebel Alliance strike force codenamed Task Force Starfall and destroyed.
